select SSEGURO,
	COD_PRODUCTO,
	PRODUCTO,	
	COD_PLAN,
	PLAN,	
	max_sid 
from
(select SSEGURO,
	COD_PRODUCTO,
	PRODUCTO,	
	cast(COD_PLAN as INTEGER) as COD_PLAN,
	PLAN,
		
		LKP_MAX_KEY.max_sid 
		from
(
SELECT 	T1.SSEGURO,
		T2.SPRODUC AS COD_PRODUCTO,
		T3.TTITULO AS PRODUCTO,
		T2.CACTIVI AS COD_PLAN,
		T4.TTITULO AS PLAN
		
FROM cdp_stg_dwh.base_lib T1	
LEFT JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SEGUROS T2 ON	T1.SSEGURO = T2.SSEGURO
LEFT JOIN cdp_ods.sisaxis_titulopro T3 ON T2.CTIPSEG = T3.CTIPSEG 
AND		T2.CRAMO = T3.CRAMO
AND		T2.CMODALI = T3.CMODALI
AND		T2.CCOLECT = T3.CCOLECT
LEFT JOIN cdp_ods.sisaxis_activisegu T4 ON T4.CRAMO = T2.CRAMO 
AND		T4.CACTIVI = T2.CACTIVI
ORDER BY T1.SSEGURO)src
left outer join 
(select 1 dummy,max(productos_lib_key) max_sid  from  cdp_stg_dwh.productos_lib) LKP_MAX_KEY
on LKP_MAX_KEY.dummy=1)
where SSEGURO is not null
